# Expert Consultation

Call `tapps_consult_expert(question)` for domain guidance.

## Built-in Expert Domains (17)

- security, performance-optimization, testing-strategies, code-quality-analysis
- software-architecture, development-workflow, data-privacy-compliance
- accessibility, user-experience, documentation-knowledge-management
- ai-frameworks, agent-learning, observability-monitoring
- api-design-integration, cloud-infrastructure, database-data-management, github

## TheStudio Custom Domains (6)

Defined in `.tapps-mcp/experts.yaml`. RAG-backed with architecture docs.

| Domain | When to use |
|--------|-------------|
| `intent-specification` | Intent layer: goals, constraints, AC, non-goals, scope boundaries |
| `agent-roles-routing` | Agent roles, overlays, EffectiveRolePolicy, tool allowlists |
| `verification-qa` | Verification Gate, QA layer, loopbacks, defect taxonomy |
| `workflow-orchestration` | Temporal workflows, retry/timeout, correlation_id, TaskPacket lifecycle |
| `epic-planning` | Persona chain (Saga/Helm/Meridian), epic structure, sprint goals, OKRs |
| `publisher-github` | Publisher, draft PRs, evidence comments, GitHub App, webhooks |

## Usage

Provide a clear question and optionally specify the domain:

```
tapps_consult_expert(
    question="How should I handle auth tokens?",
    domain="security"
)
```

```
tapps_consult_expert(
    question="What loopback count should Phase 0 use?",
    domain="verification-qa"
)
```

Use `tapps_manage_experts(action="list")` to see all available domains.

Returns RAG-backed expert guidance with confidence scores.
